headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Rollins (ROL) After Strong Multi‑Year Share Price Gains?
summary: If you are wondering whether Rollins at around US$62.73 is offering fair value or looking pricey right now, this article will walk you through what the numbers are actually saying. The stock has recent returns of 3.4% over 7 days, 4.1% over 30 days, 6.3% year to date, 31.1% over 1 year, and 80.7% over 3 years, with a 5 year return of 80.4%.
